user.bio: Untappd Moderator (M2) Melbourne, Australia. Lover of all things beer! Beer ratings and descriptions are my own.

items.checkin_comment: This was a very pleasant surprise. For a sessionable pale ale with a low ABV, it's really well put together with plenty of sweet hoppy flavours. Would love a case of this as my summer session beer. Great stuff.
